  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study compares both clinical effectiveness and cost-effectiveness of a brief,
      intensified therapy and diagnostic method for patients with mood and/or anxiety disorders
      with Treatment As Usual (TAU) at five outpatient Mental Healthcare Centers in the
      Netherlands.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
